eta[q_]:= q^(1/24)*QPochhammer[q]; e72a:= q^(1/2)*((eta[q^2]*eta[q^3]^2 *eta[q^12]^2*eta[q^18])/(eta[q]*eta[q^4]*eta[q^6]^2*eta[q^9]*eta[q^36])); a[n_]:= SeriesCoefficient[e72a, {q, 0, n}]; Table[a[n], {n,0,50}] (* _G. C. Greubel_, Feb 18 2018 *)
